  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing the Application**\n\nI\'m ready to begin designing the web application! The user wants a travel website specifically for Umrah. The requirements include all the standard sections, and crucially, they want detailed company identity and legality sections, which is very important in Indonesia. I will start by focusing on the structure of the site.\n\n\n**Adding Package Options**\n\nI\'ve been concentrating on the package options, incorporating details like hotel ratings and flight information. I\'m also carefully avoiding a generic AI aesthetic. My focus is on beautiful typography, a rich color palette, and engaging interactions. I will include dynamic filters, interactive sliders, clean spacing, and well-structured visual boxes, to create a sophisticated user experience. Finally, a visible floating WhatsApp CTA will be added for easy communication.\n\n\n**Structuring the UI Components**\n\nI\'m now building out the component structure. I\'m focusing on modularity to sidestep token limitations. I\'m creating `src/types.ts` for data definitions and `src/data.ts` to house content like profiles and package details. UI components will be modular and defined in various files. Specifically, `Header.tsx`, `Hero.tsx`, `Legality.tsx`, `PackageCard.tsx`, `PackageSection.tsx`, and `CostEstimator.tsx`, will be created. The focus is to create elegant visual components.\n\n\n**Developing Interactive Components**\n\nI\'m now focusing on interactive components, such as a custom trip calculator for Thawaf Wada services and extra days, complete with dynamic pricing and a \"Book customized trip to WA\" button, creating a highly personalized feel. I\'ve defined detailed steps and document requirements in `src/components/Requirements.tsx`, showcased testimonials with visual review stars and dates in `Testimonials.tsx`, and implemented an accordion FAQ in `FAQ.tsx`. The footer will have dummy company info and a mock responsive map, along with a high-converting, floating WhatsApp chat bubble, will be created. I\'m prioritizing the generation of appealing visuals, possibly photorealistic golden hour shots, to complete the user interface.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will generate a premium, high-quality cinematic hero banner of Masjid al-Haram in Mecca during golden hour sunrise using the `generate_image` tool to make the website\'s design look bespoke, authentic, and high-end (not like generic AI-styled stock images). This image will serve as the spectacular background of the hero section."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 4
      nanos: 921029891
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
