        }
        lines {
          text: "    id: \"faq-1\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    question: \"Apakah PT Al-Haramain Mulia Wisata sudah memiliki izin resmi PPIU?\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    answer: \"Ya, Al-Haramain Umrah beroperasi di bawah PT Al-Haramain Mulia Wisata dengan izin resmi dari Kementerian Agama Republik Indonesia (Kemenag) Penyelenggara Perjalanan Ibadah Umrah (PPIU) No. 129 Tahun 2024. Anda dapat memverifikasi legalitas kami langsung melalui aplikasi umrah resmi Kemenag (Pusaka atau Siskopatuh).\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    category: \"umum\""
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  },"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  {"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    id: \"faq-2\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    question: \"Apa saja dokumen yang harus disiapkan untuk mendaftar?\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    answer: \"Dokumen yang wajib disiapkan adalah: (1) Paspor asli dengan masa berlaku minimal 8 bulan sebelum keberangkatan dan nama minimal berisi 2 kata, (2) Kartu Keluarga (KK) asli & KTP untuk validasi pendaftaran, (3) Buku Nikah asli bagi pasangan suami istri, (4) Pasfoto terbaru latar belakang putih fokus wajah 80% ukuran 4x6 sebanyak 4 lembar, (5) Kartu Vaksin covid (jika diminta regulasi terbaru).\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    category: \"dokumen\""
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  },"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  {"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    id: \"faq-3\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    question: \"Bagaimana sistem pembayaran dan pelunasannya?\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    answer: \"Sistem pembayaran kami sangat transparan: (1) Membayar Uang Muka (DP) sebesar Rp 5.000.000 per orang untuk mengamankan seat penerbangan & hotel, (2) Pembayaran tahap dua dicicil sesuai kesepakatan, (3) Pelunasan wajib diselesaikan maksimal 45 hari sebelum tanggal jadwal keberangkatan untuk keperluan penerbitan visa dan tiket.\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    category: \"pembayaran\""
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  },"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  {"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    id: \"faq-4\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    question: \"Di mana lokasi pembekalan (Manasik) Umrah dilakukan dan berapa kali?\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    answer: \"Manasik Umrah dilaksanakan sebanyak 2 kali. Manasik pertama bertempat di ruang pertemuan kantor pusat kami atau hotel berbintang setaraf, membahas rukun ibadah fiqih dan tata cara ibadah praktis. Manasik kedua dilaksanakan 1 hari sebelum keberangkatan di hotel bandara transit, mencakup pembagian paspor, koper kabin, serta pemantapan praktis berpakaian ihram.\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    category: \"umum\""
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  },"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  {"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    id: \"faq-5\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    question: \"Apakah harga paket sudah termasuk seluruh perlengkapan umrah?\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    answer: \"Betul sekali. Harga paket yang kami cantumkan bersifat ALL-IN, di mana Anda telah mendapatkan koper fiber beroda 24 inch, tas selempang paspor, kain ihram & sabuk (untuk jamaah pria), mukena & bergo (untuk jamaah wanita), kain batik seragam esklusif, buku panduan doa saku, audio receiver guide salat, dan kantong sandal sandang.\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    category: \"fasilitas\""
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  },"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "  {"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    id: \"faq-6\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    question: \"Bagaimana jika jamaah membatalkan keberangkatan karena sakit atau urusan mendesak?\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
