  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Bento Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bento Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#FDFBF7] text-[#2C3E50] font-sans flex flex-col p-6 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Header Section -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-6\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-[#1E3A34] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37] font-serif text-2xl\\\">A</div>\\n      <div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-xl font-serif font-bold text-[#1E3A34] leading-none\\\">PT. AMANAH WISATA</h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#8B7355]\\\">Izin Kemenag No. 123/2024</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <nav class=\\\"flex space-x-6 text-sm font-medium text-[#5D4037]\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Beranda</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Paket Umroh</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Jadwal Keberangkatan</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Tentang Kami</a>\\n    </nav>\\n    <a href=\\\"https://wa.me/6281234567890\\\" class=\\\"bg-[#25D366] text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-full flex items-center space-x-2 font-bold shadow-lg hover:bg-[#128C7E] transition-colors\\\">\\n      <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 fill-current\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path d=\\\"M12.031 6.172c-2.32 0-4.591 1.255-4.591 3.945 0 1.954 1.282 3.149 1.282 3.149l-.588 2.152 2.279-.599s.931.503 1.618.503c2.321 0 4.591-1.255 4.591-3.945 0-2.69-2.27-3.905-4.591-3.905zM12 2C6.477 2 2 6.477 2 12c0 1.891.524 3.66 1.434 5.168L2 22l4.981-1.309C8.381 21.437 10.113 22 12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2z\\\"/></svg>\\n      <span>Konsultasi WA</span>\\n    </a>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <!-- Bento Grid Content -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-6 gap-4\\\">\\n    \\n    <!-- Hero / Main Package -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-7 row-span-4 bg-[#1E3A34] rounded-[2rem] p-8 text-white relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-end\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-[#D4AF37] opacity-10 rounded-full -mr-20 -mt-20\\\"></div>\\n      <span class=\\\"bg-[#D4AF37] text-[#1E3A34] px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold w-fit mb-4\\\">BEST SELLER 2024</span>\\n      <h2 class=\\\"text-5xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 leading-tight\\\">Umroh Syawal <br/>Penuh Berkah</h2>\\n      <p class=\\\"text-white/80 text-lg mb-6 max-w-md\\\">Perjalanan spiritual 9 hari dengan akomodasi hotel bintang 5 tepat di depan Masjidil Haram.</p>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-8\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/50 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Mulai Dari</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\\\">Rp 28.5 Jt</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"border border-white/30 px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium\\\">Lihat Detail Paket</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Secondary Package -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-5 row-span-3 bg-white border border-[#E5E1DA] rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-[#1E3A34]\\\">Paket VIP Itikaf</h3>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[#D4AF37] font-bold\\\">Bintang 5</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <ul class=\\\"space-y-3 mb-6 flex-1\\\">\\n        <li class=\\\"flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 italic\\\"><span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#D4AF37] rounded-full mr-2\\\"></span> Pesawat Saudia Airlines Direct</li>\\n        <li class=\\\"flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 italic\\\"><span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#D4AF37] rounded-full mr-2\\\"></span> Hotel Makkah: Hilton Suite</li>\\n        <li class=\\\"flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 italic\\\"><span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#D4AF37] rounded-full mr-2\\\"></span> Pembimbing Asatidz Sunnah</li>\\n      </ul>\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#F9F7F2] p-4 rounded-2xl flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-[#1E3A34]\\\">Rp 42.0 Jt</span>\\n        <button class=\\\"text-[#1E3A34] font-bold text-sm underline\\\">Pilih Slot</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Stat Card -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-2 row-span-2 bg-[#D4AF37] rounded-[2rem] p-6 text-[#1E3A34] flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center\\\">\\n      <p class=\\\"text-4xl font-serif font-bold\\\">5k+</p>\\n      <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter opacity-70\\\">Jamaah Terlayani</p>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Mini Feature / Location -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-2 bg-white border border-[#E5E1DA] rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center mb-2\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-[#1E3A34] mr-2\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z\\\"/><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\\\"/></svg>\\n        <span class=\\\"font-bold text-[#1E3A34]\\\">Head Office</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#8B7355] leading-relaxed\\\">\\n        Menara Amanah Lt. 12, Kav. 55<br/>\\n        Jl. Sudirman, Jakarta Selatan\\n      </p>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Trust Pilot / Quote -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-4 row-span-2 bg-[#E9E1D4] rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex items-center space-x-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-full border-2 border-[#D4AF37] flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[#1E3A34]\\\">HJ</div>\\n      <div>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-sm italic font-serif text-[#1E3A34] mb-1 leading-snug\\\">\\\"Pelayanan luar biasa, dari manasik hingga pulang ke tanah air dibimbing sangat sabar.\\\"</p>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#8B7355]\\\">\342\200\224 Ibu Hj. Siti Fatimah</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Contact Info -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-8 row-span-1 bg-white border border-[#E5E1DA] rounded-full px-8 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex space-x-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center text-xs font-medium\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[#D4AF37] mr-2\\\">EMAIL:</span> info@amanahwisata.id</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center text-xs font-medium\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[#D4AF37] mr-2\\\">HOTLINE:</span> (021) 788-9900</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center text-xs font-medium\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[#D4AF37] mr-2\\\">IG:</span> @amanahwisata.umroh</div>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-2\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#8B7355] uppercase\\\">Terdaftar Resmi</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Footer -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"mt-6 flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] text-[#8B7355] border-t border-[#E5E1DA] pt-4\\\">\\n    <p>\302\251 2024 PT Amanah Wisata - Solusi Perjalanan Ibadah Anda</p>\\n    <p>Haji Khusus & Umroh Berizin Resmi Kemenag RI</p>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Bento Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bento Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#FDFBF7] text-[#2C3E50] font-sans flex flex-col p-6 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Header Section -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-6\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-[#1E3A34] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#D4AF37] font-serif text-2xl\\\">A</div>\\n      <div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-xl font-serif font-bold text-[#1E3A34] leading-none\\\">PT. AMANAH WISATA</h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#8B7355]\\\">Izin Kemenag No. 123/2024</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <nav class=\\\"flex space-x-6 text-sm font-medium text-[#5D4037]\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Beranda</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Paket Umroh</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Jadwal Keberangkatan</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Tentang Kami</a>\\n    </nav>\\n    <a href=\\\"https://wa.me/6281234567890\\\" class=\\\"bg-[#25D366] text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-full flex items-center space-x-2 font-bold shadow-lg hover:bg-[#128C7E] transition-colors\\\">\\n      <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 fill-current\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path d=\\\"M12.031 6.172c-2.32 0-4.591 1.255-4.591 3.945 0 1.954 1.282 3.149 1.282 3.149l-.588 2.152 2.279-.599s.931.503 1.618.503c2.321 0 4.591-1.255 4.591-3.945 0-2.69-2.27-3.905-4.591-3.905zM12 2C6.477 2 2 6.477 2 12c0 1.891.524 3.66 1.434 5.168L2 22l4.981-1.309C8.381 21.437 10.113 22 12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2z\\\"/></svg>\\n      <span>Konsultasi WA</span>\\n    </a>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <!-- Bento Grid Content -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-6 gap-4\\\">\\n    \\n    <!-- Hero / Main Package -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-7 row-span-4 bg-[#1E3A34] rounded-[2rem] p-8 text-white relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-end\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-[#D4AF37] opacity-10 rounded-full -mr-20 -mt-20\\\"></div>\\n      <span class=\\\"bg-[#D4AF37] text-[#1E3A34] px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold w-fit mb-4\\\">BEST SELLER 2024</span>\\n      <h2 class=\\\"text-5xl font-serif font-bold mb-4 leading-tight\\\">Umroh Syawal <br/>Penuh Berkah</h2>\\n      <p class=\\\"text-white/80 text-lg mb-6 max-w-md\\\">Perjalanan spiritual 9 hari dengan akomodasi hotel bintang 5 tepat di depan Masjidil Haram.</p>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-8\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/50 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Mulai Dari</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#D4AF37]\\\">Rp 28.5 Jt</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"border border-white/30 px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium\\\">Lihat Detail Paket</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Secondary Package -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-5 row-span-3 bg-white border border-[#E5E1DA] rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-[#1E3A34]\\\">Paket VIP Itikaf</h3>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[#D4AF37] font-bold\\\">Bintang 5</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <ul class=\\\"space-y-3 mb-6 flex-1\\\">\\n        <li class=\\\"flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 italic\\\"><span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#D4AF37] rounded-full mr-2\\\"></span> Pesawat Saudia Airlines Direct</li>\\n        <li class=\\\"flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 italic\\\"><span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#D4AF37] rounded-full mr-2\\\"></span> Hotel Makkah: Hilton Suite</li>\\n        <li class=\\\"flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 italic\\\"><span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#D4AF37] rounded-full mr-2\\\"></span> Pembimbing Asatidz Sunnah</li>\\n      </ul>\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#F9F7F2] p-4 rounded-2xl flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-[#1E3A34]\\\">Rp 42.0 Jt</span>\\n        <button class=\\\"text-[#1E3A34] font-bold text-sm underline\\\">Pilih Slot</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Stat Card -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-2 row-span-2 bg-[#D4AF37] rounded-[2rem] p-6 text-[#1E3A34] flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center\\\">\\n      <p class=\\\"text-4xl font-serif font-bold\\\">5k+</p>\\n      <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter opacity-70\\\">Jamaah Terlayani</p>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Mini Feature / Location -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-2 bg-white border border-[#E5E1DA] rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center mb-2\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-[#1E3A34] mr-2\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z\\\"/><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\\\"/></svg>\\n        <span class=\\\"font-bold text-[#1E3A34]\\\">Head Office</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#8B7355] leading-relaxed\\\">\\n        Menara Amanah Lt. 12, Kav. 55<br/>\\n        Jl. Sudirman, Jakarta Selatan\\n      </p>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Trust Pilot / Quote -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-4 row-span-2 bg-[#E9E1D4] rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex items-center space-x-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-full border-2 border-[#D4AF37] flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[#1E3A34]\\\">HJ</div>\\n      <div>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-sm italic font-serif text-[#1E3A34] mb-1 leading-snug\\\">\\\"Pelayanan luar biasa, dari manasik hingga pulang ke tanah air dibimbing sangat sabar.\\\"</p>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#8B7355]\\\">\342\200\224 Ibu Hj. Siti Fatimah</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Contact Info -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-8 row-span-1 bg-white border border-[#E5E1DA] rounded-full px-8 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex space-x-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center text-xs font-medium\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[#D4AF37] mr-2\\\">EMAIL:</span> info@amanahwisata.id</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center text-xs font-medium\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[#D4AF37] mr-2\\\">HOTLINE:</span> (021) 788-9900</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center text-xs font-medium\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[#D4AF37] mr-2\\\">IG:</span> @amanahwisata.umroh</div>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-2\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#8B7355] uppercase\\\">Terdaftar Resmi</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Footer -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"mt-6 flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] text-[#8B7355] border-t border-[#E5E1DA] pt-4\\\">\\n    <p>\302\251 2024 PT Amanah Wisata - Solusi Perjalanan Ibadah Anda</p>\\n    <p>Haji Khusus & Umroh Berizin Resmi Kemenag RI</p>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
